Get substances from an XML version of the PSMV

Source: R/psmv-xml.R
psmv_xml_get_substances.Rd

Get substances from an XML version of the PSMV

Usage

psmv_xml_get_substances(psmv_xml = psmv_xml_get())

Arguments

psmv_xml

An object as returned by 'psmv_xml_get'

Examples

psmv_xml_get_substances()
